channel.title: Port Forwarding - READ!
channel.description:
Ok, I've already opened up ports on my other router, but now that I switched because of real-life problems, I can't get my new one to open one up! It's so frustrating and I"m sure I'm typing in the same thing as I did with my other one. I'm using linksys and I was using D-Link. Here is to show you what I have typed in.
[URL=http://imageshack.us][IMG]http://img174.imageshack.us/img174/5705/portstuffov2.jpg[/img][/URL]
In the black, I have my "IPv4 Address." Does any one see a single thing wrong with this? Plus, my no-ip is updated to my IP and I'm pretty sure it isn't the no-ip.
If you got any ideas what so ever on what it could be, pm me please or post. Thanks!
